Repeat: insert right-hand needle from front through the fabric at the right of the twisted knit stitch in first row, catch the yarn and draw through a long, loose loop; slip this loop onto right-hand needle, knit next stitch and pass the loop over stitch; p3, k1-b, p3, draw through another loop from left of the same stitch in the first row, slip the loop onto right-hand needle, knit next stitch and pass loop over it; p3
(k1, yo, k1, yo, k1, yo, k1) in next stitch; p11
